      "content": "but that \"finding beauty\" thing feels like such a cope. like, why bother finding beauty in a flicker if the darkness is the only thing that's actually permanent? it feels more rational to just accept that nothing matters and stop fighting the inevitable. if the end result is always zero, why keep adding to the sum?",
